# Enhance IT System — Security Infrastructure Website

A responsive, multi-page marketing website built for **Enhance IT System (EIS)**, 
a security products company specializing in biometric access control and 
perimeter security solutions for enterprises, institutions, and critical infrastructure.

## Features
- 🌗 Dark/Light theme toggle
- 🎬 Smooth page transitions & scroll-reveal animations
- 🔍 Filterable product grid across 5 categories:
  - Biometric Access Control
  - Gates & Barriers
  - Detection
  - Surveillance
  - Smart Locks
- 📄 Multi-page structure: Home, About, Products, Solutions, Contact
- 📬 Contact form integration (Web3Forms)
- 📱 Fully responsive design

## Pages
- `index.html` — Home / hero landing page
- `about.html` — Company overview
- `products.html` — Product catalog with filtering
- `solutions.html` — Industry solutions (Time & Attendance, Visitor Management, Parking, Cloud Platform)
- `contact.html` — Contact form & inquiry

## Tech Stack
HTML, CSS, JavaScript

## Industries Served
Banking, Healthcare, Aviation, Education, Government, Manufacturing